@Node Main "RFC 1413 Authentication Daemon for AmiTCP/IP"

	@{b}IdentD V1.2@{ub}
	===========

A @{"RFC 1413" link "rfc1413/Main"} compliant Authentication Daemon for @{b}AmiTCP/IP 4.x@{ub}

	@{" Purpose " link "Purpose"}
	@{" Features " link "Features"}

	@{" Installation " link "Installation"}
